# --- Screencasts and large media ---
# Do NOT commit video files. They bloat the repo and GitHub rejects files >100MB.
# Upload screencasts to YouTube (unlisted), Loom, or Google Drive and put the
# LINK in your submission / PORTFOLIO.md instead.
*.mp4
*.mov
*.mkv
*.webm
*.avi
*.cast

# --- Secrets: never commit private keys ---
# Your cloud-init file may reference your PUBLIC key (safe). Never commit a
# PRIVATE key. These patterns block the common ones.
id_rsa
id_ed25519
id_ecdsa
*.pem
*_private*
*.key

# --- OS / editor / agent noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
.claude/
.cursor/
.aider*

# --- Scratch ---
scratch/
tmp/
*.log

# --- UAT / persona test run (never commit) ---
# Per-lab reports + captured terminal output from the end-to-end
# student-persona walkthrough. Used to evaluate the labs from a
# first-time student's perspective; not part of the instructional
# materials.
test/
